    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Complexes within an enclosure, comprising single or multi-unit family dwellings with communal spaces, adjacent outbuildings or structures. Examples are in Africa.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
